## 2. Technical Pillars (Vetted & Hardened)

### 2.1 Hardware Integrity (L0/L1)
- **Silicon Standardization**: All Tier-1 sensors (VFA, LRZ, PFA) standardized on **nRF52840** for secure hardware-signing.
- **Root-of-Trust**: Every node utilizes **AES-256 hardware encryption** for all telemetry before it leaves the sensor housing.
- **BOM Maturity**: High-fidelity, COTS-optimized BOM developed for the CSU SLV RC pilot, eliminating "Vaporware" risk.

### 2.2 Protocol & Consensus (L2)
- **AllianceChain**: Verified the **PBFT (Practical Byzantine Fault Tolerance)** consensus mechanism for the DHU/RSS ledger. 
- **Temporal Drift Fix**: Implemented atomic locking and timezone-aware UTC for all financial and hydrological data (Transaction Finality).
- **Network Resilience**: Mesh-topology at the edge ensures 2,000-acre coverage without dead spots, reporting back to the **Sovereign-Grade Hub (PMT)**.

### 2.3 Logic & Algorithmic Vetting (L3)
- **Kriging Engine**: Audit of the 1m-fidelity spatial interpolation logic. Verified that ground-truth "Truth Points" (VFA) correctly anchor the "Dumb Nodes" (LRZ) to meet **Water Court Standards of Admissibility**.
